lead_paragraph: A judge said Thursday he will review police video made shortly after Justin Bieber's recent Miami Beach arrest to determine if some portions should be withheld from the public, particularly clips depicting the singer urinating into a cup as part of a drug test.

headline.main: Fla. Judge to Review Bieber Video Before Release
headline.print_headline: Fla. Judge to Review Bieber Video Before Release
